library(readxl)
CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT <- read_excel("CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT.xlsx")
View(CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT)

head(CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT)
CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT %>%
  filter(Question == "Percent of adults who engage in no leisure-time physical activity") %>%
  filter(YearEnd == 2017) %>%
  group_by(`Race/Ethnicity`) %>%
  summarise(mean(Data_Value, na.rm = T),
            mean(High_Confidence_Limit, na.rm = T))
CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT%>%
        ggplot(aes(Data_Value)) +
        geom_histogram() +
        labs(title = "Percent of adults who engage in no leisure-time physical activity")

ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT, aes(x = `Race/Ethnicity`, y = Data_Value)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(title = "Percent of adults who engage in no leisure-time physical activity")

ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT, aes(x = `Income`, y = Data_Value, color = Income)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  coord_flip()

  labs(title = "Percent of adults who engage in no leisure-time physical activity")

CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT %>%
  filter(Question == "Percent of adults who achieve at least 150 minutes a week of moderate-intensity aerobic physical activity or 75 minutes a week of vigorous-intensity aerobic activity (or an equivalent combination)") %>%
  filter(YearEnd == 2017) %>%
  group_by(`Race/Ethnicity`) %>%
  group_by(Gender) %>%
  summarise(mean(Data_Value, na.rm = T),
            mean(High_Confidence_Limit, na.rm = T))
  ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT, aes(x = Gender, y = Data_Value)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(title = "Percent of adults who engage in no leisure-time physical activity")

ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT) +
  geom_point(aes(x = Low_Confidence_Limit, y = High_Confidence_Limit, color = Education, size = Data_Value))

ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT) +
  geom_point(aes(x = Data_Value, y = Education))

ggplot(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT) +
  geom_point(aes(x = Data_Value, y = Education), color = "blue")

ggplot() +
  layer(data = CAP_5320_MIDTERM_PROJECT, geom = "point", stat = "identity",
        position = "identity", aes(x = YearStart, y = Data_Value))
